{"tid":543173,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夠鐘死心了","createTime":"2018-01-28T08:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T10:47:05.000Z","uid":35693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f51afcbeea87cc570623830c16b9896f5ff4f8","tid":543173,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"最近追緊個女仔<br />\n之後岩岩識果陣其實都好地地，<br />\n大家關係都幾好。<br />\n之後大家都出黎行街睇戲食下飯咁既<br />\n<br />\n之後我同佢講其實我鐘意佢<br />\n咁問題就開始出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢成日都覺得我同一時間flirt緊好多女仔<br />\n總之我一去街佢就覺得我去左溝女<br />\n大佬呀！邊有咁多女溝啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同佢講話電話無電<br />\n佢聽日要早起返工叫佢早啲訓<br />\n佢就講埋啲悔氣說話&rdquo;唔阻住你溝女&rdquo;etc...<br />\n咁掉返轉到佢出夜街佢又同返我講<br />\n&ldquo;出街唔係男就女架啦，唔通等你約咩&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之呢。。。<br />\n問題就由我同佢表白果陣開始，<br />\n我講乜佢都唔信我覺得我呃鳩佢咁<br />\n有時一兩次我都忍佢我當係港女發下癲<br />\n但成日都係咁我真係覺得好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係應該對佢死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcc96518c5f72becdb0d0b0a9e10acbc3edc69a","tid":543173,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0193d925bdae5c1b94c88658a6dbfe4d2e184dae","tid":543173,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"樓主靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f547d2c27c67f7bcda7ca677a170eff2586f599","tid":543173,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0193d925bdae5c1b94c88658a6dbfe4d2e184dae","tid":543173,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"樓主靚仔<img src=\